The woman apparently sped off in her car after the fight with her ex in hot pursuit, News24 reported.He allegedly tried to force her car off the road causing the vehicle to crash into a boundary fence. The woman was slightly injured and was taken to hospital News24 said.It said the man had then fled the scene and caused another accident between a car and a taxi resulting in 18 people being injured who had to be ferried to hospital in three ambulances.The man was apparently also taken to hospital according to the news medium.